Cornbread buns were baked in the town of [[Shadowdale]] in the [[Dalelands]] and served by a platterful. [[Storm Silverhand]] liked to eat her corn bread [[cheese]]-laced.

[[Vaasa]]n cornbread was served as a dessert, covered in colorful artistically layered frosting, sometimes white and pink color.

In the [[Vast]], corn bread could be found in the town of [[Suiter's Hill]] – the region's only producer of Maztican maize.{{Cite organized play/LC/Out in the Cornfield|10}}
